data.description: Nestled on just under an acre and down a quiet street, lovely rose gardens and fruit trees await in this well maintained 4 BR/2BA manufactured home on a foundation.  Open kitchen/dining and family room with separate living room.  Spacious master bedroom with walk-in closet and garden tub.  A variety of storage opportunities throughout the home.  Breezeway connects garage to home. Backyard includes automatic sprinklers, and an extra storage shed.  No HOA.  CCR’s allow for one horse or one cow per parcel.
